## CRITICAL — General rules
- Each data key should map to at most ONE field. Never reuse the same value for unrelated fields.
- Match semantically, not literally. A data key like "phone" maps to a field labeled "Phone number" or "Mobile".
- For boolean/Yes-No data keys, map them DIRECTLY without inverting. If the data says "Yes", select "Yes".
